In this life, I will avenge myself!
Gu Tianlang, the Lord of the Underworld, died under the siege of cultivators and the trial of Heaven. 500 years later, he is reincarnated because of Nirvana Jade, the only item preserved in the Heavenly Tribulation. Having lost everything, he is determined to avenge himself in this life.
(Source: Manta)
Moto Saikyou no Kenshi wa, Isekai Mahou ni Akogareru

One day, Soma learns that he was reincarnated from a powerful swordsman. In this life, however, all he wants is to master magic! When he learns that he has no skills at all in this life, he gets left behind by his family. With no magic spells, most would assume he'll never be able to cast even a single spell, but Soma isn't ready to take "no" for an answer...
(Source: Sol Press)
